<h1>Specify colors using RGB values</h1>

<h2 style="background-color:rgb(255, 0, 0);">rgb(255, 0, 0)</h2>
<h3 style="background-color:rgb(0, 0, 255);">rgb(0, 0, 255)</h3>
<h4 style="background-color:rgb(60, 179, 113);">rgb(60, 179, 113)</h4>
<h5 style="background-color:rgb(238, 130, 238);">rgb(238, 130, 238)</h5>
<h6 style="background-color:rgb(255, 165, 0);">rgb(255, 165, 0)</h6>


<h1>Make transparent colors with RGBA-opacity</h1>

<h2 style="background-color:rgba(255, 99, 71, 0);">rgba(255, 99, 71, 0)</h2>
<h3 style="background-color:rgba(255, 99, 71, 0.2);">rgba(255, 99, 71, 0.2)</h3>
<h4 style="background-color:rgba(255, 99, 71, 0.4);">rgba(255, 99, 71, 0.4)</h4>
<h5 style="background-color:rgba(255, 99, 71, 0.6);">rgba(255, 99, 71, 0.6)</h5>
<h6 style="background-color:rgba(255, 99, 71, 0.8);">rgba(255, 99, 71, 0.8)</h6>


